esolution%20%E2%80%94%20very%20simple%20in%20theory%20but%20incredibly%20powerful%20in%20practice.%20Most%20companies%20don't%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20rule%3A%20No%20bringing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ceo-mark-zuckerberg-management-style-direct-reports-delegation-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edirect%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Everyone%20in%20the%20room%20is%20expected%20to%20know%20the%20discussion's%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20trying%20to%20literally%20force%20the%20VPs%20to%20solve%20it%20themselves%20because%20I%20want%20them%20to%20be%20in%20the%20details.%20So%2C%20you're%20not%20allowed%20to%20bring%20anyone%20else%20in%20to%20explain%20your%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20S%C3%B6derstr%C3%B6m%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20be%20on%20top%20of%20it%20enough%20to%20explain%20it%20to%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20direct%20reports%20coming%20and%20going%2C%20the%20same%20group%20shows%20up%20each%20week.%20Over%20time%2C%20it%20becomes%20a%20tight-knit%2C%20high-trust%20team%2C%20S%C3%B6derstr%C3%B6m%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpotify%20and%20S%C3%B6derstr%C3%B6m%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fcd0706-3810-4643-b667-256d6173edeb%5C%22%3ESpotify's%20'bets'%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20marathon%20Tuesday%20sessions%20are%20part%20of%20what%20Spotify%20calls%20its%20%26quot%3Bbets%26quot%3B%20process%20%E2%80%94%20a%20structured%20way%20of%20deciding%20what%20the%20company%20builds%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20six%20months%2C%20each%20VP%20pitches%20a%20bet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20much%20like%20a%20startup%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20S%C3%B6derstr%C3%B6m%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20get%20to%20use%20the%20fact%20that%20Gustav%20or%20Alex%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-ceo-daniel-ek-feels-inadequa