-huawei-single-most-formidable-tech-company-in-china-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHuawei%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20again%20called%20the%20latter%2C%20which%20builds%20its%20own%20chips%2C%20%26quot%3Bformidable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20competition%20in%20China%20is%20really%20intense%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%20The%20CEO%20also%20said%20the%20US%20has%20no%20monopoly%20on%20AI%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPower%20is%20quite%20cost-effective%20in%20China%2C%20and%20there's%20plenty%20of%20land.%20So%20the%20ban%20on%20H20%20is%20not%20effective%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20added%20that%20there%20was%20no%20way%20to%20further%20%26quot%3Bdegrade%26quot%3B%20the%20company's%20current%20graphics%20processing%20unit%20architecture%20such%20that%20buyers%20would%20want%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBouts%20of%20broad%20market%20and%20tech%20sell-offs%20and%20angst%20about%20export%20controls%2C%20among%20other%20issues%2C%20have%20depressed%20investor%20darling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently.%20The%20company's%20shares%20are%20up%20nearly%2041%25%20in%20the%20past%20year%20but%20flat%20this%20year%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-chip-export-rules-china-failure-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747804509000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682d5757ac40ae2b0c9e9cf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-chip-export-rules-china-failure-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Nvidia%20CEO%20says%20that%20Chinese%20tech%20companies%20have%20benefited%20from%20the%20US%20crackdown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan%2CMeghan%20Morris)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C