0Tesla%20for%20at%20least%20five%20more%20years%2C%20and%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-austin-tesla-robotaxis-self-driving-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erobotaxis%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20rolled%20out%20in%20June%20as%20previously%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20no%20doubt%20about%20that%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20during%20a%20video%20call%20when%20asked%20about%20his%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20shares%20remained%20mostly%20unchanged%20after%20markets%20closed%20Tuesday%2C%20but%20they%20rebounded%20in%20May%20compared%20to%20previous%20months%20after%20Musk%20said%20he%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-stepping-back-doge-tesla-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escale%20back%20his%20involvement%20with%20DOGE%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20April%2022.%20However%2C%20Tesla%20shares%20are%20still%20down%20in%202025%20thus%20far%2C%20following%20revenue%20and%20income%20declines%20in%20Q1.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20main%20takeaways%20on%20robotics%20from%20Musk's%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228724f4d9-a171-4c6d-8757-9f2d1ebac233%5C%22%3EA%20'prudent'%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20was%20asked%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-fsd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETesla's%20Full%20Self-Driving%20Supervised%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20software%20running%20a%20red%20light%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-vs-waymo-full-self-driving-fsd-robotaxi-lidar-cameras-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20test%20drive%20by%20BI%20reporters%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20stressed%20the%20slow%20rollout%20of%20robotaxis%20for%20safety%20reasons%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20prudent%20for%20us%20to%20start%20with%20a%20small%20number%2C%20confirm%20that%20things%20are%20going%20well%2C%20and%20then%20scale%20it%20up%20proportionate%20to%20how%20well%20we%20see%20it's%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20told%20CNBC%20host%20David%20Faber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20they%20are%20now%20testing%20robotaxis%20%26quot%3Bdriving%2024%2F7%20with%20drivers%20in%20the%20cars%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3Bessentially%20no%20interventions%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20he%20prefers%20caution%20because%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20first%20introduction%20of%20unsupervised%20full%20self-driving.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20deliberately%20take%20it%20slow%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20could%20start%20with%201%2C000%20or%2010%2C000%20on%20day%20one%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20would%20be%20prudent.%20So%20we%20will%20start%20with%20probably%2010%20for%20a%20week%2C%20then%20increase%20it%20to%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20that%20the%20goal%20would%20be%20to%20have%201%2C000%20robotaxis%20within%20a%20few%20months%20in%20Austin%2C%20before%20expanding%20the%20operation%20to%20other%20cities%20like%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20San%20Antonio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Musk%20did%20not%20directly%20address%20BI's%20reporting%20that%20the%20FDS%20made%20a%20critical%20error%2C%20he%20said%20Tesla's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-robotaxi-austin-geofenced-intersections-fsd-red-light-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erobotaxis%20will%20be%20geo-fenced%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20select%20areas%20of%20Austin.%20Alphabet's%20Waymo%20also%20limits%20its%20autonomous%20cars%20to%20specific%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20going%20to%20take%20intersections%20unless%20we%20are%20highly%20confident%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20told%20Faber.%20%26quot%3BOr%20it%20will%20just%20take%20a%20route%20around%20that%20intersection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-