ly.%20The%20humanoid%20robot%20Optimus%20needs%20to%20perform%20the%20task%20that%20it's%20being%20asked%20to%20perform%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20told%20Nadella.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228763279e-e10a-44b9-9fac-e5465e6240d5%5C%22%3EThe%20market%20reacts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20media%20blitz%20generated%20a%20lukewarm%20response%20from%20investors.%20Tesla%20shares%20rose%20around%200.5%25%20at%20market%20closing%20on%20Tuesday%20compared%20to%20the%20day%20before%2C%20but%20stocks%20began%20to%20dip%20in%20the%20after-hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20teased%20his%20plan%20to%20bring%20humanoid%20robots%20to%20market%20for%20years.%20In%202021%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musks-ai-day-tesla-bot-is-just-a-guy-in-a-bodysuit-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edancing%20actor%20in%20a%20body%20suit%3C%2Fa%3E%20gave%20us%20our%20first%20look%20at%20Optimus%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Tesla%20Bot.%20By%202022%2C%20a%20rough%20prototype%20was%20up%20and%20walking%20at%20the%20company's%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Day%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202024%2C%20Business%20Insider's%20Hasan%20Chowdhury%20reported%20that%20Tesla's%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-optimus-humanoid-robots-robotaxi-day-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erobotics%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20advanced%20since%20its%20early%20days.%20Chowdhury%20reported%20that%20Optimus%20prototypes%20at%20last%20year's%20Tesla's%20robotaxi%20day%20played%20rock-paper-scissors%20with%20the%20audience%2C%20poured%20drinks%2C%20and%20danced%2C%20though%20some%20attendees%20thought%20the%20bots%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-robotaxi-event-optimus-robot-serves-drinks-dances-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtrolled%20by%20human%20operators%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20timeline%20goes%2C%20Musk%20sai