o%20(USA).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr%20Sharma%20has%20presented%20at%20major%20international%20forums%20such%20as%20the%20Cambridge%20Particle%20Meeting%2C%20IAQM%20(UK)%2C%20World%20Environment%20Expo%202022%2C%20Smart%20Cities%20Conference%20New%20Delhi%202017%20and%20several%20other%20conferences%20across%20Australia%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Egypt%2C%20UK%20and%20the%20U.S.%20His%20expertise%20spans%20air%20quality%2C%20exposure%20science%2C%20urban%20sustainability%2C%20and%20public%20health.%20He%20is%20passionate%20about%20bridging%20science%2C%20policy%2C%20and%20community%20action%20to%20build%20cleaner%2C%20healthier%20cities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A0%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faarohan.infosys.org%2F%3Fcmpid%3Dsco_TheBetterIndia_EB_AarohanAwards25_foundation_banner_24042025_lq_Awareness_Rgn%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20in%20a%20two-part%20series%20exploring%20how%20India%20can%20build%20cleaner%2C%20more%20just%2C%20and%20breathable%20cities%20by%20putting%20people%2C%20not%20policies%2C%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20climate%20action.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhat%20if%20the%20fight%20for%20clean%20air%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20emissions%20and%20enforcement%2C%20but%20about%20strollers%2C%20footpaths%2C%20and%20the%20quiet%20resilience%20of%20everyday%20people%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr.%20Ashish%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20global%20research%20labs%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20smog-choked%20streets%20reveals%20a%20truth%20we%20often%20overlook%3A%20real%20change%20begins%20when%20science%20meets%20empathy.%20In%20a%20world%20where%20babies%20breathe%20in%20more%20pollutants%20than%20their%20parents%20and%20the%20urban%20poor%20suffer%20silently%20while%20policies%20stall%2C%20Sharma%20shows%20us%20how%20citizen%20science%2C%20behavioural%20shifts%2C%20and%20grassroots%20innovation%20can%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20cities%20that%20not%20only%20survive%20but%20breathe.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20global%20labs%20to%20local%20streets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20we%20make%20our%20cities%20cleaner%2C%20our%20air%20safer%2C%20and%20our%20communities%20stronger%3F%20After%20spending%20over%20a%20decade%20working%20in%20laboratories%2C%20classrooms%2C%20field%20projects%2C%20and%20ministries%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20answers%20lie%20not%20only%20in%20data%20or%20policy%20but%20also%20in%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20journey%20from%20academic%20labs%20in%20the%20UK%20(University%20of%20Surrey%2C%20Guildford)%2C%20Australia%20(Macquarie%20University%2C%20Sydney)%2C%20South%20Korea%20(Gwangju%20Institute%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology)%2C%20and%20the%20US%20(University%20of%20Toledo%2C%20Ohio)%20to%20the%20bustling%20lanes%20of%20Delhi%20(TRIPP%20IIT%20Delhi)%20and%20Aligarh%20(Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20Aligarh%2C%20UP)%20has%20taught%20me%20that%20urban%20sustainability%20is%20not%20just%20a%20scientific%20puzzle%20but%20a%20deeply%20human%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20piece%2C%20I%20want%20to%20share%20the%20lessons%20I%E2%80%99ve%20gathered%20through%20research%2C%20risk%2C%20and%20real-world%20engagement%20about%20how%20cleaner%20air%20and%20more%20livable%20cities%20are%20not%20distant%20dreams%20but%20within%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20hidden%20emergency%20in%20our%20breath%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20pollution%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20knock%20on%20your%20door.%20It%20seeps%20in%20quietly%E2%80%94through%20windows%2C%20lungs%2C%20and%20childhoods.%20In%20India%2C%20it%20contributes%20to%20nearly%20one%20in%20every%20ten%20deaths.%20During%20my%20PhD%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20groups%E2%80%94babies%20in%20prams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20findings%20were%20startling%3A%20children%20in%20prams%20are%20exposed%20to%20up%20to%2060%25%20more%20pollutants%20than%20adults.%20Their%20breathing%20height%20puts%20them%20right%20in%20line%20with%20vehicle%20exhaust.%20Some%20children%20face%20up%20to%2072%25%20higher%20pollution%20levels%20simply%20based%20on%20where%20they%20sit%20in%20a%20double%20pram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20knowledge%20alone%20isn%E2%80%99t%20power.%20Action%20is.%20So%20we%20created%20practical%2C%20scalable%20interventions%E2%80%94pram%20covers%2C%20urban%20route%20mapping%2C%20low-cost%20sensors%E2%80%94and%20tested%20them%20in%20real-world%20conditions.%20The%20Mitigating%20Air%20Pollution%20Exposure%20(MAPE)%20project%2C%20funded%20by%20UKRI%2C%20was%20not%20just%20a%20research%20study.%20It%20became%20a%20guide%20for%20urban%20parents%20navigating%20toxic%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20insights%20shaped%20public%20conversations%2C%20informed%20policies%2C%20and%2C%20perhaps%20most%20importantly%2C%20gave%20families%20the%20tools%20to%20protect%20their%20children%20now%2C%20not%20just%20in%20the%20distant%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20in%20prams%20breathe%20up%20to%2060%25%20more%20pollutants%20than%20adults%20%E2%80%94%20and%20up%20to%2072%25%20more%20in%20double%20prams%2C%20simply%20due%20to%20their%20height%20and%20position%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T182931.653_11zon-1747746013-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-435346%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDuring%20his%20PhD%2C%20Dr%20Ashish%20found%20that%20babies%20in%20prams%20inhale%20up%20to%2060%25%20more%20pollution%20than%20adults.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr.%20Ashish%20Sharma%2C%20together%20with%20his%20PhD%20supervisor%20Prof.%20Prashant%20Kumar%2C%20was%20featured%20during%20a%20BBC%20visit%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey%20campus%2C%20highlighting%20their%20innovative%20experimental%20setup%20for%20air%20pollution%20monitoring%20using%20electric%20bike%20trailers.%20Prof.%20Prashant%20Kumar%20is%20the%20Co-Director%20of%20the%20Institute%20for%20Sustainability%2C%20Professor%20and%20Chair%20in%20Air%20Quality%20and%20Health%2C%20and%20Founding%20Director%20of%20the%20Global%20Centre%20for%20Clean%20Air%20Research%20(GCARE)%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey%2C%20Guildford%2C%20UK.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FQydeRKs6p0A%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22University%20of%20Surrey's%20Research%20on%20Babies%20Exposure%20in%20Bike-trailers%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Surrey%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20also%20studied%20the%20efficacy%20of%20face%20masks%20during%20pollution%20peaks.%20Our%20GCARE%20team%20found%20that%20while%20FFP3%20respirators%20filtered%20nearly%2097%25%20of%20harmful%20particles%2C%20medical%20and%20cloth%20masks%20offered%20moderate%20protection.%20This%20work%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20helped%20inform%20personal%20protection%20strategies%20for%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20real%20impact%20happens%20when%20citizens%20become%20scientists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5fDWMmMHpe8%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22IAQM%20Webinar%3A%20Mitigating%20Air%20Pollution%20Exposure%20to%20the%20Young%20Children%20(MAPE)%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20science%20stays%20on%20paper%2C%20people%20pay%20the%20price%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20mountains%20of%20data%20and%20well-meaning%20policies%2C%20the%20gap%20between%20research%20and%20action%20remains%20wide.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20founded%20Sustainability%20Alternatives%20UK%20%E2%80%94%20to%20turn%20insights%20into%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChampioning%20the%20twin%20transition%20for%20SMEs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%2021%20February%202023%2C%20I%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20speaking%20at%20a%20webinar%20hosted%20by%20the%20Institution%20of%20Environmental%20Sciences%20(IES)%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%9CSMEs%20Twin%20Transition%3A%20Towards%20Sustainability%20and%20Digital%20Transformation.%E2%80%9D%20As%20the%20Founding%20CEO%20of%20Sustainability%20Alternatives%20Ltd.%20(UK)%20and%20a%20Principal%20Research%20Scientist%20at%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20I%20took%20this%20opportunity%20to%20spotlight%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%20(SMEs)%20in%20shaping%20resilient%2C%20future-ready%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20talk%2C%20I%20emphasised%20an%20increasingly%20urgent%20truth%3A%20the%20convergence%20of%20sustainability%20and%20digital%20innovation%20is%20no%20longer%20optional%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20existential.%20Especially%20in%20the%20context%20of%20post-pandemic%20recovery%2C%20SMEs%20cannot%20afford%20to%20view%20sustainability%20and%20digital%20transformation%20as%20luxuries.%20These%20are%20the%20pillars%20that%20will%20determine%20their%20survival%20and%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20also%20wanted%20to%20challenge%20a%20prevailing%20misconception%20%E2%80%94%20that%20sustainability%20is%20a%20domain%20exclusive%20to%20large%20multinational%20corporations.%20I%20firmly%20believe%20that%20if%20we%20are%20serious%20about%20inclusive%20progress%2C%20we%20must%20democratise%20both%20sustainability%20and%20digital%20inclusion.%20SMEs%20are%20the%20backbone%20of%20most%20economies.%20Leaving%20them%20behind%20means%20leaving%20behind%20the%20communities%2C%20jobs%2C%20and%20innovations%20that%20they%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Empowering%20SMEs%20with%20green%20tech%20and%20digital%20tools%20is%20key%20to%20building%20sustainable%2C%20future-ready%20economies.%20(Representational%20picture%20source%3A%20Shutterstock)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-435369%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20SMEs%20with%20green%20tech%20and%20digital%20tools%20is%20key%20to%20building%20sustainable%2C%20future-ready%20economies.%20(Representational%20picture%20source%3A%20Shutterstock)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20advocated%20for%20giving%20SMEs%20real%20access%20to%20cutting-edge%20technologies%2C%20ESG%20tools%2C%20and%20innovative%20business%20models.%20These%20resources%20are%20essential%20for%20environmental%20responsibility%20and%20carving%20out%20a%20competitive%20edge%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20session%2C%20I%20shared%20practical%20insights%20and%20explored%20promising%20tech%20solutions%20that%20can%20enable%20SME%20leaders%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%E2%80%99re%20entrepreneurs%20or%20C-suite%20executives%20%E2%80%94%20to%20take%20actionable%20steps%20forward.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20I%20called%20for%20a%20mindset%20shift%3A%20we%20must%20all%20embrace%20a%20culture%20of%20learning%2C%20unlearning%2C%20and%20relearning%20if%20we%20want%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20fast-evolving%20landscape%20of%20Industry%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20moment%20to%20build%20bridges%2C%20not%20barriers%2C%20for%20SMEs%20stepping%20into%20a%20more%20sustainable%20and%20digitally%20empowered%20future.%20And%20I%E2%80%99m%20committed%20to%20helping%20make%20that%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20collaboration%20matters%20now%20more%20than%20ever%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20local%20action%20and%20community-led%20change%20are%20powerful%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20realised%20that%20big%20impact%20often%20needs%20big%20collaboration.%20Climate%20change%2C%20water%20stress%2C%20and%20digital%20divides%20don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20at%20borders%E2%80%94and%20the%20solutions%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20either.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20regional%20cooperation%20is%20becoming%20such%20a%20critical%20piece%20of%20the%20sustainability%20puzzle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20stepping%20up%20to%20play%20a%20bigger%20role%E2%80%94not%20just%20for%20itself%2C%20but%20as%2