ering%20Gautam%E2%80%99s%20point%2C%20Gopalika%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20clear%20mismatch%20between%20investor%20expectations%20and%20the%20capital%20needs%20of%20these%20climate%20tech%20ventures.%20Investors%20in%20India%20often%20demand%20that%20startups%20build%20comprehensive%20end-to-end%20value%20chains.%20For%20example%2C%20they%20expect%20e-mobility%20companies%20to%20manage%20everything%20from%20battery%20production%20to%20vehicle%20manufacturing.%20In%20contrast%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20tech%20ecosystem%20is%20much%20more%20developed%2C%20where%20specialised%20players%20often%20dominate%20different%20segments%20of%20the%20value%20chain%2C%20which%20also%20enables%20a%20company%20to%20focus%20on%20these%20specific%20niches%20and%20innovate%20within%20those%20areas.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20expectation%20of%20broad%20scope%20innovation%20in%20India%20often%20hinders%20the%20more%20targeted%20and%20specialised%20progress%20that%20we%20see%20in%20other%20countries.%20Bridging%20these%20kinds%20of%20gaps%20requires%20very%20enhanced%20collaboration%20between%20the%20investors%2C%20the%20founders%2C%20and%20policy%20makers%20to%20sort%20of%20identify%20certain%20regulatory%20and%20policy%20barriers%20that%20hinder%20green%20capital%20flow%20and%20also%20foster%20a%20more%20conducive%20environment%20for%20scaling%20these%20sustainable%20innovations%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20also%20notes%20that%20the%20supply%20of%20domestic%20capital%20for%20climate%20tech%20startups%20is%20much%20less%20than%20what%20it%20should%20be.%20It%E2%80%99s%20what%20motivated%20Oorjan%20to%20invest%20in%20such%20startups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%